{"tid":145500,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"4月東京行程一問","createTime":"2017-03-06T10:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T03:28:50.000Z","uid":34654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f3cf18f30022a48c9a1fd9e50c66bc95abf267d","tid":145500,"uid":34654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:00:33.000Z","msg":"DAY1 20/4 夜晚6點落機 新宿食下野<br />\nDAY2 21/4築地早餐 原宿 表參道<br />\nDAY3 22/4淺草雷門 上野 Sky tree <br />\nDAY4  23/4 吉祥寺 下北澤<br />\nDAY5 24/4 箱根<br />\nDAY625/4  河口湖 <br />\nDAY7 26/4  芝櫻祭    ?<br />\nDAY8 27/4 ？<br />\nDay9 28/4 outlet  5點飛機 Hk<br />\n<br />\n1）Day5day6 我地會自駕遊 會係箱根同河口湖過一晚夜 唔知大家會有咩景點推介 ？想去大涌谷 同天上公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2）另外想問下芝櫻祭有冇野睇？如果唔係80%或滿開係咪唔值得去呢？<br />\n3）因為我柒下柒下book錯左時間 day7-day9有冇酒店推介？同埋仲有咩地方好玩？我諗緊住返新宿定係住成田機場附近 玩下成田周圍好？唔知大家又點睇呢？<br />\n4）同埋我係咪買Tokyo Subway Ticket就係基本可以去晒我以上所講既地方？<br />\n好多問題問 唔該晒大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7142d41b3c739fc58156b85528d61f7ca5354f64","tid":145500,"uid":34654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:02:50.000Z","msg":"同埋想問下自駕times或toyota 比較好呢？"},{"pid":"dc1664cc9116bbafdef4633b68f872f1453eda7a","tid":145500,"uid":21624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:08:36.000Z","msg":"其他答你唔到<br />\n4) day2 3 可以用到 day4 就淨係用到去涉谷果程，我諗你買48小時就夠"},{"pid":"e3027131ce7e312e5f5caadd91722218e792abea","tid":145500,"uid":72739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:09:54.000Z","msg":"我18to25 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d019acf8fd456eda450d3759a2809c43ae593fc3","tid":145500,"uid":35589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:11:35.000Z","msg":"有車牌去河口湖真係方便十鳩幾倍"},{"pid":"b4ff062e946b5310ec017a8ac9234be4a829da6b","tid":145500,"uid":72702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci